resources.string: Ukuvala kucacile. Akukho ukubuyela emuva. Uqinisekile?
Ngeke uvunyelwe ukuvula i-akhawunti entsha enegama elifanayo, noma ngabe icala lihlukile.
Ngishintshe umqondo wami, ungavali i-akhawunti yami
Uqinisekile ukuthi ufuna ukuvala i-akhawunti yakho? Ukuvala i-akhawunti yakho kuyisinqumo saphakade. AKUFANELE ukwazi ukungena ku-NJALO YONKE.
